bilingual.source: Art has the power to transform society.
Art has the power to transform emotions.
Music has the power to uplift people's moods.
bilingual.target: 音乐有能力提升人们的情绪。

bilingual.source: The assimilative power of the human brain is remarkable.
bilingual.target: 人脑的同化的能力是惊人的。

bilingual.source: The power to innovate inheres in the company's culture.
bilingual.target: 创新能力固有于公司的文化中。
经济困难压抑了他们的消费能力。

bilingual.source: The superhero's power of invisibility made him unbeatable.
bilingual.target: 超级英雄的隐形能力让他无敌。

bilingual.source: The base level of a river determines its erosive power.
bilingual.target: 河流的基准面决定了它的侵蚀能力。

bilingual.source: The computational power of modern computers is astonishing.
bilingual.target: 现代计算机的计算能力令人惊叹。

bilingual.source: Add borax to the solution to increase its cleaning power.
bilingual.target: 添加硼砂到溶液中以增强其清洁能力。

list.abstract: power，英文单词，名词、形容词、及物动词、不及物动词，作名词时意为“力量，能力；电力，功率，性能；政权，势力；[数]幂，人名；(英、葡)鲍尔”，作形容词时意为“借影响有权势人物以操纵权力的”，作及物动词时意为“激励；供以动力；使…有力量”，作不及物动词时意为“快速前进”。
power全称为Performance Optimization With Enhanced RISC，是一种由IBM设计的RISC处理器架构，被《IBM Connect电子报》于2007年8月号译为“增强RISC性能优化”。 power系列微处理器在IBM服务器、超级电脑、小型电脑及工作站中应用，广泛作为主CPU使用。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, Shaw's power is that he's a shadow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 肖的能力之强就好比他是个影子。

yingyinNormal.en: You have power yet to save your people, Sidao.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还有能力拯救你的人民，贾似道。

yingyinNormal.en: I just lost the power before I could get to it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是在找到它之前失去了这种能力。

yingyinNormal.en: So they know who you are. They want their power back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那它们知道你是谁了，它们想恢复能力。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, Element Lad's ability is the power to transmute chemical elements.
yingyinNormal.zh: 元素少年的超能力是转化化学元素。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah! What was his super power again? A superhuman thirst for knowledge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对啊，他的超能力是什么？一个渴望知识的超人。

yingyinNormal.en: So you all have the power in your own way to develop your own Angel Network.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，你们每个人都有能力打造自己的天使网络项目。

yingyinNormal.en: Regardless of that, you control the power now. Just as I did in Verdun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不管怎么样，你拥有了这个能力，就像当初我在凡尔登时一样。

yingyinNormal.en: How far will he take his power? Does he act by our will or by his own?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他会将能力使用到什么程度？他是遵从我们的意志，还是他自己的？

yingyinNormal.en: Look at me. You have the power to destroy the stone. Don't. You must do it. Wanda, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看着我。你有能力摧毁宝石。别。你必须这么做。旺达，求你。

yingyinNormal.en: He has the power to control metal. Last I checked that's what most of your weapons were made of.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他有控制金属的能力，你们的武器绝大多数都是用金属做的。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. That's true. That's true, we can do this. You're right. We can do this. We'll just power through.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，是这样。是这样，我们能行。对，对，我们能行。我们有能力渡过！

yingyinNormal.en: Human beings have a horrible track record of following people with great power down paths that led to huge human atrocities.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人类在这方面有着诸多不堪的历史，盲目追随有强大能力的人，并最终导致严重的人类暴行。

yingyinNormal.en: Energy is lost the longer electricity travels along normal power lines. This new system transmits five times the capacity of the old electricity grid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电能在通过标准输电线进行长距离输送时会有损失，而这套新的系统拥有旧电网五倍的传输能力。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, and you with it. We're not having this conversation. Eliminating the stone is the only way to be certain that Thanos can't get it. That's too high a price. Only you have the power to pay it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你也会随之被摧毁。这不是个选择。只有销毁宝石才能确保灭霸拿不到它。那代价太高了。只有你有能力付出这代价。

yingyinNormal.en: Soft power, a term I'm sure you're all familiar with at this point coined by Rhodes Scholar and Oxford alumnus Joseph Nye is defined as the ability to attract and persuade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我相信今天你们对软实力这个词都很熟悉了，这个词是由罗氏奖学金获得者，牛津校友，约瑟夫·奈发明的，含义是，吸引和说服的能力。

yingyinNormal.en: Power failure. Implementing power failure protocol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 断电了，启动断电应急预案。

yingyinNormal.en: Incredible power awaits you. Power beyond anything you can imagine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一种神功等着你去发掘，这种神功强大到你无法想像。

yingyinNormal.en: Go, go, Power Rangers, go!
yingyinNormal.zh: 走，恐龙战队，快！

yingyinNormal.en: You inherit too much power.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你继承了太多力量。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_family.mean: n. 权力；能力；本领；才智；支配力；影响力；体力；威力；力量；机械力；动力；电力；幂；乘方；指数；大量的

sense_info_list.en: possession of control, authority, or influence over others

examination_example.sentence: By the time a problem has been addressed and remedied it may have vanished, to be replaced by new abuses of <highlight>power</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当一个问题被解决和补救的时候，它可能已经消失了，取而代之的是新的滥用权力。

examination_example.sentence: Competition law appears to be the only way to address these imbalances of <highlight>power</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 竞争法似乎是解决这些权力失衡的唯一途径。

examination_example.sentence: As such, it needed to appreciate the economic realities, the social contexts and <highlight>power</highlight> relations in which each epoch stood.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，它需要理解每个时代所处的经济现实、社会背景和权力关系。

sense_info_list.en: electricity, especially when considering its use or production
sense_info_list.zh: 电力; 能源; 能量

examination_example.sentence: But a boost in the storage capacity of batteries is making their ability to keep <highlight>power</highlight> flowing around the clock more likely.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是电池存储容量的增加使得它们更有可能保持电力全天候流动。

examination_example.sentence: The conflict has been surfacing since 2002, when the corporation bought Vermont's only nuclear <highlight>power</highlight> plant.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 自2002年该公司收购佛蒙特州唯一的核电站以来，冲突就开始浮出水面。

examination_example.sentence: The hardest task that television asks of anyone is to turn the <highlight>power</highlight> off after he has turned it on.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电视要求任何人完成的最困难的任务是在他打开电源后将其关闭。

sense_info_list.zh: 体力; 威力; 力量

examination_example.sentence: Intuition's special <highlight>powers</highlight> are unleashed only in certain circumstances.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 直觉的特殊力量只有在特定的情况下才会释放出来。

examination_example.sentence: Johannes Kepler and Galileo Galilei demonstrated the <highlight>power</highlight> of scientific study and discovery.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 约翰尼斯·开普勒和伽利略·伽利雷展示了科学研究和发现的力量。

examination_example.sentence: Organizations and officials use the <highlight>power</highlight> of group dynamics to help individuals improve their lives and possibly the world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 组织和官员利用群体动力的力量来帮助个人改善他们的生活，甚至可能改善世界。

sense_info_list.en: a natural skill or an ability to do something

examination_example.sentence: The earlier they learn that they have the <highlight>power</highlight> to do that, the better.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们越早知道自己有能力做到这一点，对他们的好处就越大。

examination_example.sentence: Stereotypes associated with obesity include laziness, lack of will <highlight>power</highlight>, and lower prospects for success.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与肥胖相关的刻板印象包括懒惰、缺乏意志力和较低的成功前景。

examination_example.sentence: What it is in the <highlight>power</highlight> of each to accomplish for himself.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每个人都有能力为自己完成些什么。

sense_info_list.en: supply with a form of energy

examination_example.sentence: In Scotland, for example, wind turbines provide enough electricity to <highlight>power</highlight> 95 percent of homes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，在苏格兰，风力涡轮机为95%的家庭提供足够的电力。

examination_example.sentence: Tech giants like Microsoft are being attracted by the availability of clean energy to <highlight>power</highlight> their data centers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 像微软这样的科技巨头正被用来驱动他们的数据中心的清洁能源的可用性所吸引。

examination_example.sentence: The advance is driven in part by vehicle manufacturers, who are placing big bets on battery-<highlight>powered</highlight> electric vehicles.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一进步部分是由汽车制造商推动的，他们在电池驱动的电动汽车上下了很大的赌注。

sense_info_list.en: a nation that has influence among other nations

examination_example.sentence: The period when the United States emerged as an international <highlight>power</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国崛起为国际强国的时期。

sense_info_list.en: the rate of speed at which work is done

examination_example.sentence: Disciplined, uncritical loyalty to political <highlight>power</highlight> became his compass for the choices he had to make.

examination_example.sentence: Exaggerating the <highlight>power</highlight> of technology in shaping the world.

examination_example.sentence: Some UK cities have lobbied without success for the <highlight>power</highlight> to levy a charge on visitors.

examination_example.sentence: They will not allow any gasoline <highlight>powered</highlight> vehicle to be registered after 2030.

examination_example.sentence: Rarely has there been a better example of the <highlight>power</highlight> of attitude, one of our most powerful psychological tools.

examination_example.sentence: If that required emotional intelligence beyond the <highlight>power</highlight> of Mr. Musk's imagined machine, at least someone to chop the carrots.

examination_example.sentence: In emerging economies, rural communities are bypassing the wires and wooden poles that spread <highlight>power</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在新兴经济中，农村社区正绕过输送电力的电线和木杆。

examination_example.sentence: Those simultaneous challenges appear less overwhelming with increasingly better answers to a centuries-old question; how to make <highlight>power</highlight> portable.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从古至今，人们一直在探索如何让电力便携化。如今，人们找到了回答这一问题的更好的答案，那些伴随新技术发展而来的诸多挑战也就没那么严峻了。
